title: Ep 125 - Spirit Guides Are Real
description: Pat, Digs, Nick, Ty, Connor, Gump, Zito and Todd talk about wedding proposals, hypnotism, Nick’s plumbing issues, life after death, spirit guides, guardian angels and more.
